  "$jason": {
    "username": "ethan",
    "password": "sdn3Uef2!"
  }
}



To use this return value, you can chain another action as a 
success
 callback and use the attributes, like this:


{
  "type": "$util.alert",
  "options": {
    "title": "Sign in",
    "description": "Please enter username and password",
    "form": [{
      "name": "username"
    }, {
      "type": "secure",
      "name": "password"
    }]
  },
  "success": {
    "type": "$network.request",
    "options": {
      "url": "https://www.jasonclient.org/users/sign_in.json",
      "method": "post",
      "data": {
        "username": "{{$jason.username}}",
        "password": "{{$jason.password}}"
